msgctxt "68_Angry Ex-Employee"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "80_Akiyama"
msgid "Hey..."
msgstr "Viejo..."

msgctxt "92_Angry Ex-Employee"
msgid "Enough of this bullshit. I worked with his dad for more than thirty years."
msgstr "Estoy harto de esta mierda. Trabajé con su padre más de treinta años."

msgctxt "104_Angry Ex-Employee"
msgid "We were good friends, all of us. And then this... this\\r\n"\n"ignorant moron... He tore it all to pieces."
msgstr "Éramos como una familia. Y luego este... este\\r\n"\n"maldito hijo idiota tenía que arruinarlo todo."

msgctxt "116_60_80_MOUNTAIN_VF_OFF"
msgid "That company... That company was...\\r\n"\n"*sob*"
msgstr "Esa empresa... era todo lo que...\\r\n"\n"*sollozo*"

msgctxt "128_Shiobara"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "140_Akiyama"
msgid "It can't be easy to start over at your age. But if you're\\r\n"\n"willing to try, stop by Sky Finance on Tenkaichi Street."
msgstr "No debe ser fácil empezar de nuevo a tu edad. Pero si\\r\n"\n"de verdad quieres intentarlo, pásate por Sky Finance en\\r\n"\n"la calle Tenkaichi."

msgctxt "152_Angry Ex-Employee"
msgid "I'm just a moneylender, but a little money might be just\\r\n"\n"what you need right now."
msgstr "Solo soy un prestamista, pero a lo mejor un empujoncito\\r\n"\n"económico es lo que necesitas ahora mismo."

msgctxt "164_Angry Ex-Employee"
msgid "Sky Finance...?"
msgstr "¿Sky Finance...?"

msgctxt "176_Akiyama"
msgid "Drop by any time."
msgstr "Te estaré esperando."

msgctxt "236_Shiobara"
msgid "You knew all along. You knew that downsizing was the only way to get that company in the black."
msgstr "Lo sabías desde el principio... Sabías que reducir personal era la única manera de salvar esa empresa."

msgctxt "248_Akiyama"
msgid "Yep. Sure did."
msgstr "En efecto. Lo sabía."

msgctxt "260_Shiobara"
msgid "I knew it! Then, why? Why!?"
msgstr "Entonces, ¿por qué? ¡¿Por qué hiciste esto?!"

msgctxt "272_Akiyama"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "284_Shiobara"
msgid "His friends had been with him from the start. The president\\r\n"\n"didn't want to downsize, but that was the only way to save\\r\n"\n"his company."
msgstr "El presidente dice que no quiere echar a la gente que lo apoyó\\r\n"\n"desde el inicio, pero tiene que hacerlo para que la\\r\n"\n"empresa sea rentable."

msgctxt "296_Akiyama"
msgid "And he still couldn't bring himself to do it, so you've come\\r\n"\n"here to mull it all over, is that right?"
msgstr "No pudiste decírselo, ¿verdad?\\r\n"\n"Es por eso que estabas aquí dándole vueltas al asunto."

msgctxt "308_Shiobara"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "320_Akiyama"
msgid "That angry old man, Paradise Advertising... I imagine you\\r\n"\n"probably understand this now, but downsizing isn't\\r\n"\n"necessarily a bad thing."
msgstr "Con lo de tu padre y lo de Publicidad Paradise,\\r\n"\n"supongo que ya te diste cuenta.\\r\n"\n"Reducir personal no siempre significa algo malo."

msgctxt "332_Talk_No"
msgid "Sure, it's not always the ideal or even the only option, but\\r\n"\n"sometimes you have to do what's best for the company."
msgstr "Claro, no siempre es la opción ideal, pero a veces hay que\\r\n"\n"tomar decisiones difíciles por el bien de la empresa."

msgctxt "344_Angry Ex-Employee"
msgid "If you don't, you might end up hurting a lot more people,\\r\n"\n"like that old man."
msgstr "De lo contrario, podrías terminar lastimando a mucha más\\r\n"\n"gente, como a ese anciano."

msgctxt "356_Shiobara"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "368_Akiyama"
msgid "Do you see what I'm trying to say?"
msgstr "¿Entiendes lo que intento decir?"

msgctxt "380_Shiobara"
msgid "Akiyama-san... Could you ask that leaflet company guy to\\r\n"\n"come meet us here?"
msgstr "Akiyama-san... ¿Sería tan amable de contactar al director\\r\n"\n"de la empresa de folletos y pedirle que venga?"

msgctxt "392_Akiyama"
msgid "Sure. I'll call him right now."
msgstr "Claro. Lo llamaré ahora mismo."

msgctxt "440_Akiyama"
msgid "Yes, hello? This is Akiyama from Sky Finance. We have\\r\n"\n"something we'd like to talk to you about... Could you come\\r\n"\n"meet us at the park?"
msgstr "¿Presidente? Habla Akiyama de Sky Finance.\\r\n"\n"Tenemos algo que nos gustaría discutir con usted...\\r\n"\n"¿Podría venir al parque?"

msgctxt "584_Paradise Advertising President"
msgid "What is it, Akiyama-san? Is something wrong?"
msgstr "¿Qué sucede, Akiyama-san? ¿Pasó algo?"

msgctxt "596_Akiyama"
msgid "Shiobara-kun wants to talk to you."
msgstr "Shiobara-kun quiere hablar contigo."

msgctxt "608_Shiobara"
msgid "Uh, well... I once brought down my father's printing company\\r\n"\n"because I didn't want to downsize and lose all of the good\\r\n"\n"people he'd employed over the years..."
msgstr "Verá... cometí un error en el pasado. Me negaba a despedir a\\r\n"\n"la buena gente que trabajó durante años en la empresa de\\r\n"\n"mi padre, y terminé llevándola a la quiebra..."

msgctxt "632_Paradise Advertising President"
msgid "Yes... I thought as much. But my people have been with me\\r\n"\n"since the beginning. How could I just force them out like\\r\n"\n"that?"
msgstr "Sí... Lo entiendo... Pero son como mi familia...\\r\n"\n"¿Cómo se supone que los eche a la calle así sin más?"

msgctxt "644_Shiobara"
msgid "If the business fails, that's it! Everything's over! All of\\r\n"\n"your employees get hurt－every last one of them!"
msgstr "¡Si la empresa quiebra, se acabó! ¡¡Todos tus empleados\\r\n"\n"saldrán perdiendo, ninguno se salvará!!"

msgctxt "656_Paradise Advertising President"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "668_Shiobara"
msgid "I understand it's a tough decision to make, but it's the\\r\n"\n"president's responsibility to protect the company..."
msgstr "Por eso, aunque sea un decisión difícil, el presidente\\r\n"\n"debe hacerlo... Tiene que velar por la supervivencia\n"\n"de su empresa."

msgctxt "680_Paradise Advertising President"
msgid "Akiyama-san?"
msgstr "¿Akiyama-san?"

msgctxt "692_Akiyama"
msgid "I agree. Downsizing's the only option. My heart goes out to\\r\n"\n"you, but it's got to be better than turning everybody out\\r\n"\n"into the streets."
msgstr "Concuerdo. Reducir personal es la única opción. Siento\\r\n"\n"mucho lo que estás pasando, pero es mejor que dejar\\r\n"\n"a todo el mundo en la calle."

msgctxt "704_Paradise Advertising President"
msgid "I see. I guess that really is the only way to go, then..."
msgstr "Ya veo. No queda otra opción, por mucho que me duela..."

msgctxt "716_Shiobara"
msgid "I just have one favor to ask of you."
msgstr "Sólo tengo un favor que pedirle."

msgctxt "728_Angry Ex-Employee"
msgid "If this downsizing does turn your company around, make sure\\r\n"\n"the people who were forced out get first crack at working\\r\n"\n"for you again."
msgstr "Si esta reducción de personal logra salvar su empresa, no\\r\n"\n"olvide a aquellos que se tuvieron que ir. Deles prioridad\\r\n"\n"para volver a trabajar con usted."

msgctxt "740_Talk_No"
msgid "After all, it's those employees who served the company by\\r\n"\n"leaving, and they'd all been friends and coworkers for a\\r\n"\n"long time..."
msgstr "Incluso si terminaron siendo despedidos,\\r\n"\n"ellos incluso contribuyeron a la empresa con su renuncia.\\r\n"\n"Recuerde que son amigos, como su familia..."

msgctxt "752_Paradise Advertising President"
msgid "All right. I promise I will."
msgstr "Está bien. Te prometo que lo haré."

msgctxt "764_Talk_No"
msgid "When I first met you, Shiobara-san, I'd assumed you were\\r\n"\n"nothing more than some half-baked smartass. But now I see\\r\n"\n"that you look out for everyone like a fine, upstanding CEO."
msgstr "Shiobara-san, cuando te conocí, pensé que eras un tipo\\r\n"\n"arrogante y charlatán. Pero ahora veo que eres un\\r\n"\n"director ejemplar, que cuida de su gente y su sustento."

msgctxt "776_Talk_Ojigi"
msgid "I know it's awfully hard, but we've got to do the best we\\r\n"\n"can by our employees. Now, if you'll excuse me..."
msgstr "Es una decisión dura, pero debemos velar por el bienestar\\r\n"\n"de nuestros trabajadores. Ahora, si me disculpan..."

msgctxt "788_Shiobara"
msgid "Thank you very much. I've learned a lot from all of this..."
msgstr "M-muchas gracias. He aprendido mucho de todo esto..."

msgctxt "800_Akiyama"
msgid "Paradise Advertising will be in the black soon enough, so\\r\n"\n"let's consider the test passed. The money is yours, provided\\r\n"\n"you're still interested?"
msgstr "Veo un futuro brillante para Publicidad Paradise, así que\\r\n"\n"considero esta prueba superada. ¿Sigues queriendo\\r\n"\n"el préstamo?"

msgctxt "812_Shiobara"
msgid "Yes, I am. I can't give up now."
msgstr "Sí, lo quiero. No puedo rendirme ahora."

msgctxt "824_Talk_Yes"
msgid "I still don't know what kind of company to build, but I'm\\r\n"\n"going to do my best to make sure it brings happiness to\\r\n"\n"everyone who works there. I can promise you that much!"
msgstr "Todavía no tengo claro qué tipo de empresa crear, pero\\r\n"\n"me aseguraré de que la gente que trabaje allí sea lo más\\r\n"\n"feliz posible. ¡Esa es mi promesa!"

msgctxt "836_Akiyama"
msgid "And for right now, that's enough. Here you are, then. Five\\r\n"\n"million yen."
msgstr "Eso es más que suficiente por ahora.\\r\n"\n"Toma, aquí tienes los cinco millones."

msgctxt "848_Shiobara"
msgid "Thank you so much! I'm going to give it everything I've got!"
msgstr "¡Muchísimas gracias! ¡Me esforzaré al máximo!"

msgctxt "860_Akiyama"
msgid "Um... This is all I've got, but I'd like you to at least have\\r\n"\n"some token of my gratitude. Please accept it along with my\\r\n"\n"thanks!"
msgstr "Sé que no es mucho, pero quiero expresarle mi más\\r\n"\n"profundo agradecimiento. ¡Por favor, acepte este pequeño\\r\n"\n"obsequio!"

msgctxt "896_Akiyama"
msgid "Sure, why not? Thank you kindly."
msgstr "Claro, ¿por qué no? Muchas gracias."

msgctxt "908_Shiobara"
msgid "All right, I'm off! I'm about to become a very busy man!"
msgstr "¡Bueno, me voy! ¡Voy a estar muy ocupado a partir de ahora!"

